All functions

calc_bins

Calculates bins (breaks) based on standard deviations of Box-Cox power-transformed data for mapping

calc_effective_extent

Calculate and map effective extent of selected centroids

calc_full_extent

Calculates spatial extent of non-zero data from Raster* object for plotting

compute_ppms

Computes the Predictive Performance Metrics for a spatiotemporal extent

data_st_subset

Spatiotemporal subsetter for eBird Status and Trends products table

download_data

Downloads data package for a single species or for the example data

label_raster_stack

Labels 52 week RasterStack with the dates for each band

load_pds

Load partial dependencies for single species eBird Status and Trends products

load_pis

Load predictor importances for single species eBird Status and Trends products

map_centroids

Map PI and PD centroid locations

parse_raster_dates

Parses the names attached to a Raster* from label_raster_stack()

plot_all_ppms

Plot all predictive performance metrics

plot_binary_by_time

Plot binary occurrence metrics by time

plot_pds

Plot partial dependency as line plot

plot_pis

Plot predictor importances as barplots

raster_st_subset

Spatiotemporal subsetter for eBird Status and Trends products raster

runs_w_names

Data frame of species available
